  "title": "Lorry Driver class 3",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p> Daily delivery of frozen / chilled goods to various locations island-wide, in 14-feet</p><p>refrigerator trucks</p><p> Responsible for executing day-to-day delivery schedule</p><p> Maintain cleanliness and good condition of the vehicle at all times</p><p> Fulfil any urgent / ad-hoc deliveries as instructed by supervisor</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p> Singapore Class 3 Driving License</p><p> Can cope with the physical demands of the job, e.g., carry heavy goods (at least</p><p>25kg)</p><p> Good work attitude</p><p> Able to drive 14-feet trucks</p><p><strong>Location:</strong> West of Singapore</p><p><strong>Work hours:</strong> 9am to 6pm, 6-day work week (including public holidays)</p><p><strong>Others:</strong></p><p> Company transport available from Admiralty MRT (for day shift)</p><p>Job Types: Full-time, Permanent</p><p>Benefits:</p><ul><li>Food provided</li></ul><p>Work Location: In person<br /></p><p>Chan Wei Wen, Mervyn (Reg. No: R25149588)</p><p>ST Venture EmPloyment Agency (EA License No: 09C5583)</p><p>Please send an updated resume to stvea888@gmail.com if you are keen to apply for this position</p>",
